raph.co.uk/culture/culturevideo/filmvideo/7501431/Kick-Ass-premiere-in-London.html |accessdate=2019-10-20 |date=2010-03-22 |work=''The Telegraph'' |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140818114649/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/culturevideo/filmvideo/7501431/Kick-Ass-premiere-in-London.html |archive-date=2014-08-18 }}</ref>。接著，該片於3月26日開始在英國院線上映<ref>{{Cite web |title=Kick-Ass superheroes 'are real people' and 'can die' |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/article/10071434/kick-ass-superheroes-are-real-people-and-can-die |accessdate=2019-10-20 |date=2010-03-23 |last=Wilson |first=Ollie |work=BBC |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181109155931/http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/article/10071434/kick-ass-superheroes-are-real-people-and-can-die |archive-date=2018-11-09 }}</ref>，美國的檔期則位在稍晚的4月16日<ref name="BOM-Preview" />。[[美國電影協會|美國電影協會]]（MPAA）以片中有「極為暴力的場面、大量髒話、性愛場面、裸露鏡頭及有關毒品的內容——其中有部分牽扯到兒童」為由將電影評為R級，意味著17歲以下觀眾需要有家長或成年監護人陪同才能觀看<ref name="RT">{{Cite web |title=Kick-Ass (2010) |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1217700_kick_ass? |accessdate=2018-01-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171228110703/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1217700_kick_ass |archivedate=2017-12-28 |website=Rotten Tomatoes |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[英國電影分級委員會|英國電影分級委員會]]（BBFC）把《特攻聯盟》分為[[電影分級制度#英国|15級]]，理由為片中含有「極多的髒話及漫畫風格的暴力場面」<ref name="runtime" />。導演[[馬修·范恩|馬修·范恩]]認為BBFC的分級正確無誤<ref name="Times Online-Interviews" />。

