《特攻聯盟》的[[數碼多功能影音光碟|DVD]]及[[藍光光碟|藍光光碟]]於2010年8月3日在北美地區推出<ref name="DVD/BD">{{Cite web |title=Kick-Ass (2010) |url=https://www.dvdsreleasedates.com/movies/1311/Kick-Ass.html |accessdate=2018-01-25 |publisher=DVDsReleaseDates.com |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6wqZInNUN?url=https://www.dvdsreleasedates.com/movies/1311/Kick-Ass.html |archivedate=2018-01-30 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，於發行首週賣出約43萬份DVD<ref name="The Numbers DVD/BD">{{Cite web |title=Kick-Ass (2010) Video sales |url=https://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Kick-Ass#tab=video-sales |accessdate=2018-01-25 |publisher=[[The_Numbers_(網站)|The Numbers]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170723091229/http://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Kick-Ass#tab=video-sales |archivedate=2017-07-23 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，在DVD銷售榜上名列第一<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.cnbc.com/id/38821668 |title=Lionsgate's Blockbuster defense vs. Icahn |last=Boorstin |first=Julia |date=2010-08-23 |publisher=CNBC |accessdate=2010-08-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121016125459/http://www.cnbc.com/id/38821668 |archivedate=2012-10-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodnews.com/2010/08/12/kick-ass-debuts-at-number-one-on-the-dvd-sales-chart/ |title="Kick-Ass" debuts at number one on the DVD sales chart |date=2010-08-12 |work=HollywoodNews.com |accessdate=2010-08-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161219205127/http://www.hollywoodnews.com/2010/08/12/kick-ass-debuts-at-number-one-on-the-dvd-sales-chart/ |archivedate=2016-12-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/kick-ass-kicks-aside-competitors-26575 |title='Kick-Ass' kicks aside competitors on charts |last=Prange |first=Stephanie |date=2010-08-11 |publisher=''The Hollywood Reporter'' |accessdate=2019-10-27 |archive-date=2021-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120055306/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/kick-ass-kicks-aside-competitors-26575 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而藍光光碟則賣出約24萬份<ref name="The Numbers DVD/BD"/>。截至2020年7月，該片已在家庭媒體方面收穫了約3,969萬美元的收益<ref name="The Numbers DVD/BD"/>。在英國，電影的家庭媒體於2010年9月6日發行<ref name="UK-DVD">{{Cite news |url=http://www.syfy.co.uk/blog/exclusive-kick-ass-concept-art |title=Exclusive – Kick-Ass Concept Art |publisher=Syfy |accessdate=2010-08-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101207031652/http://www.syfy.co.uk/blog/exclusive-kick-ass-concept-art |archivedate=2010-12-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。據《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》報導，《特攻聯盟》的家庭媒體發售後掀起了一波[[邪典追捧|邪典追捧]]<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://herocomplex.latimes.com/movies/kick-ass-2-aaron-taylor-johnson-talks-comic-book-sequel-and-that-avengers-role/#/0 |title='Kick-Ass 2': Aaron Taylor-Johnson returns, 'Avengers' rumors swirl |last=Millar |first=DiAngelea |date=2013-08-14 |work=''Los Angeles Times'' |accessdate=2014-04-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170630183258/http://herocomplex.latimes.com/movies/kick-ass-2-aaron-taylor-johnson-talks-comic-book-sequel-and-that-avengers-role/#/0 |archivedate=2017-06-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

